            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(SN) Die veneris qui fuit undecimus intrantis mensis septembris. <rs
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines">Bonorum virorum</rs> presentia quorum
                        nomina inferius scripta invenirentur, domnus <persName
                            key="#Abbots #Monasteries" ref="#people/4025">Lambertus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Abbots #Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/2007">Sancte
                            Marie</orgName> de <placeName key="#Monasteries" ref="#places/2479"
                            >Filonica</placeName>, iussione <persName
                            key="#Bishops #Mother_churches #Dioecesis" ref="#people/3532"
                            >Manfredi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">œpiscopi</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Mother_churches #Dioecesis" ref="#juridical_persons/1426"
                            >sanctę <placeName
                                key="#Mother_churches #Dioecesis #Bishops #Burgi #Cities"
                                ref="#places/275">Mantuanensis</placeName> æcclesię</orgName>, finem
                        fecit in manu donni <persName key="#Priors #Monasteries" ref="#people/3570"
                            >Wilielmi</persName>, <rs key="#Priors">prioris</rs> monasterii <orgName
                            key="#Priors #Monasteries #Monks" ref="#juridical_persons/2001"> Sancti
                            Benedicti</orgName> quod est hædificatum iuxta <placeName key="#Rivers"
                            ref="#places/4196"><rs key="#Rivers">flumen</rs> Padi</placeName>,
                        adstante ibi domno <persName key="#Monks"><name ref="Adam/monacus"
                                >Adam</name></persName> et domno <persName key="#Monks"><name
                                ref="Stephanus/monacus">Stefano</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Monks">monachi</rs> ipsius monasterii Sancti Benedicti, vice
                        ipsius monasterii, nominative de <rs>lite</rs> illa quam adversus ipsum
                        monasterium movebat vel movere potuisset ipse Lambertus suosque fratres de
                            <rs key="#Churches">æcclesia</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/2491">Sanctę
                            Marię</orgName>
                        <placeName key="#Churches" ref="#places/1591">Caput Mincii</placeName> et de
                        æcclesia <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/2078">Sancti
                            Sili</orgName>, et de possessionibus ipsis æcclesiis pertinentibus in
                            <placeName
                            key="#Churches #Islands #Landed_possessions #Forests #Shores #Fisheries #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos"
                            ref="#places/2400"><rs key="#Islands">insula</rs> Sancti
                            Benedicti</placeName>, in <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Forests">silvis</rs>, <rs key="#Shores">ripis</rs>, rupinis, <rs
                            key="#Fisheries">piscationibus</rs> ac <rs
                            key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">paludibus</rs>; et insuper de omnibus
                        litibus quas adversus ipsum monasterium movere potuisset ex parte ipsius
                        monasterii Sanctę Marię Filonice de aliqua re et possessione in predicta
                        insula existente, tali modo quod ipse Lambertus abbas suique fratres
                        eorumque successores per se vel per sunpmissas personas ipsum monasterium
                        Sancti Benedicti exinde amplius non molestaverint. Si vero ipse donnus
                        Lambertus abbas suique fratres eorumque successores contra hanc finem
                        predictam fecerint, tunc ipso monasterio Sancti Benedicti componere debent
                            <rs key="#Penalty">nomine poene libras quinquaginta denariorum
                            Mediolanensium</rs>, et poena saluta taciti tamen omni tempore permanere
                        debent propri. Hanc antem finem accepit ipse domnus Lambertus abbas ex parte
                        domni Wilielmi prioris monasterii Sancti Benedicti libras decem denariorum
                        Mediolanensium, quas idem abbas solvit Adam de Gauso pro recuperanda
                        possessione Sancti Victoris, quam pro pignore ex parte ipsius abbatis
                        habebat. Actum est hoc in <rs key="#Burgi">burgo</rs>
                        <rs key="#Cities">civitatis</rs> Mantuę, in claustro <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2416">Sancti Martini</orgName>. Anno domnice
                        incarnationis millesimo centesimo trigesimo sexto, predicto die, indictione
                        quartadecima. <rs key="#Witness">Interfuerunt</rs> ibi <persName
                            key="#Witness #Boni_viri/boni_homines"><name ref="Wibertus/de Ingebaldo"
                                >Wibertus de Ingelbaldo</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Boni_viri/boni_homines"><name ref="Robawettone"
                                >Robawettone</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Boni_viri/boni_homines"><name
                                ref="Arnaldus/de Bernardo Scazo">Arnaldus de Bernardo
                            Scazo</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Boni_viri/boni_homines"><name ref="Lanfrancus"
                                >Lanfrancus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#siblingOf"/>frater <persName key="#siblingOf"><name ref="Morandus"
                                >Morandi</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Boni_viri/boni_homines"><name ref="Petrus/Calarius"
                                >Petrus Calarius</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Boni_viri/boni_homines"><name ref="Lanfredus"
                            />Landefredus</persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Boni_viri/boni_homines"><name ref="Teobaldus/de Bergamo"
                                >Teutaldus</name></persName> de <placeName ref="#places/10"
                            >Bergamo</placeName>, <persName><name ref="Albertus/de Brentario"
                                >Albertus</name></persName> de Brentario, <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Gherardus/de Ficarolo">Homodeus</name></persName> de
                            <placeName ref="#places/77">Figariole</placeName> et rogati sunt testes.
                        Ego Lambertus abbas ecclesie Sancte Marie de Felonica huic <rs
                            key="#Cartula">cartule transaccionis</rs> a me facte subscripsi. Et ego
                            <persName key="#Witness #Monks #Priests"><name
                                ref="Rodelandus/monachus et presbiter">Rolandus</name></persName>
                        monachus et <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs> indignus huic cartule
                        subscribo. Et ego <persName key="#Witness #Monks #Priests"><name
                                ref="Petrus/monachus et presbiter">Petrus</name></persName>
                        presbiter et monachus modo huic cartule transaccionis subscripsi. Ego
                        <persName key="#Advocatus #Witness" ref="#people/4026">Casotus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Advocatus">advocatus</rs> uic cartule translactionis subscripsi.
                        Et ego <persName key="#Witness #Monks"><name ref="Gherardus/monachus"
                                >Gerardus</name></persName> monachus huic cartule transaccionis
                        subscripsi. Et ego <persName><name ref="Martinus/monachus"
                            >Martinus</name></persName> monachus huic cartule transaccionis
                        subscripsi. (SN) Ego <persName key="#Notary #Writer" ref="#people/3573"
                            >Bonus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> his interfui rogatus <rs key="#Writer"
                            >scripsi</rs>. </ab>
                </div>
